commit.message:
(default_compilers): For output of as when -c is not used,

use %g, rather than %b, because the file is going to be deleted anyway.

From-SVN: r1783

files.patch:
@@ -428,7 +428,7 @@ static struct compiler default_compilers[] =
 		   %{pg:%{fomit-frame-pointer:%e-pg and -fomit-frame-pointer are incompatible}}\
 		   %{S:%W{o*}%{!o*:-o %b.s}}%{!S:-o %{|!pipe:%g.s}} |\n\
               %{!S:as %{R} %{j} %{J} %{h} %{d2} %a %Y\
-		      %{c:%W{o*}%{!o*:-o %w%b.o}}%{!c:-o %d%w%b.o}\
+		      %{c:%W{o*}%{!o*:-o %w%b.o}}%{!c:-o %d%w%g.o}\
                       %{!pipe:%g.s} %A\n }}}}"},
   {"-",
    "%{E:cpp -lang-c %{nostdinc*} %{C} %{v} %{A*} %{D*} %{U*} %{I*} %{i*} %{P} %I\
